0may%20sound%20like%20a%20choice%20nobody%20would%20make%2C%20but%20some%20young%20people%20are%20voluntarily%20choosing%20to%20become%20NEETs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20acronym%20stands%20for%20people%20who%20are%20not%20in%20employment%2C%20education%2C%20or%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20their%20numbers%20are%20on%20the%20rise.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Filostat.ilo.org%2Fblog%2Fassessing-the-current-state-of-the-global-labour-market-implications-for-achieving-the-global-goals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInternational%20Labour%20Organization%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%20a%20fifth%20of%20people%20between%2015%20and%2024%20worldwide%20in%202023%20were%20considered%20NEETs%2C%20a%20level%20not%20seen%20in%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20extended%20periods%20off%20from%20employment%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20momentum%2C%20a%20psychologist%20says%20they%20could%20also%20have%20some%20positive%20mental%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b710582d-d86f-4469-80b4-706b32485616%5C%22%3EThe%20rise%20of%20the%20voluntary%20NEETs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennial-neets-happy-idle-until-finding-right-job-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESome%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20reclaiming%20the%20NEET%20label%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20social%20media%2C%20believing%20that%20being%20voluntarily%20dormant%20is%20more%20appealing%20than%20taking%20the%20first%20job%20that%20they%20can%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20Warner%2C%20a%20psychologist%20and%20business%20consultant%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20grind%20culture%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US%20where%20people%20think%20working%20harder%20yields%20better%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20newer%20generation%20is%20starting%20to%20have%20a%20different%20spin%20on%20how%20they%20view%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apa.org%2Fpubs%2Freports%2Fwork-in-america%2F2023-workplace-health-well-being%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20American%20Psychological%20Association's%202023%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2077%25%20of%20workers%20reported%20feeling%20stressed%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20we'll%20just%20grind%20through%20it%2C%20get%20over%20with'%2C'%26quot%3B%20Warner%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20some%20individuals%20are%20saying%2C%20'No%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20actually%20take%20the%20time%20for%20myself%2C%20reduce%20some%20stress%2C%20some%20anxiety%2C%20some%20depressive%20symptoms%20to%20protect%20my%20overall%20mental%20well-being.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMental%20health%20and%20a%20work-life%20balance%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-managers-are-doing-things-differently-seems-to-be-paying-off-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehuge%20priorities%20for%20many%20Gen%20Zers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20they%20are%20keen%20to%20work%20at%20organizations%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-advocate-mental-health-flexibility-workplace-management-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempathetic%20values%20and%20flexibility%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20Zoomers%20and%20millennials%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-increasingly-no-income-cannot-retire-or-buy-houses-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Blost%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bdisconnected%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20struggle%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce%20or%20find%20themselves%20suddenly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-won-great-resignation-now-losing-the-big-firing-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20career%20and%20recruitment%20specialists%20told%20BI%20being%20a%20NEET%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20mistake%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20result%20of%20%26quot%3Bunrealistic%20views%26quot%3B%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20reality%26quot%3B%20about%20how%20career%20opportunities%20come%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20big%20gaps%20on%20someone's%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20could%20be%20a%20red%20flag%20to%20potential%20employers%2C%20and%20that%20sometimes%2C%20fulfillment%20comes%20from%20putting%20yourself%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20Warner%2C%20waiting%20a%20bit%20longer%20to%20find%20a%20job%20that%20aligns%20with%20your%20values%20and%20identity%20creates%20fulfillment%20in%20life%20and%20can%20mitigate%20burnout%20and%20other%20%26quot%3Blong-term%20psychological%20challenges.%26quot%3B%20It%20can%20also%20boost%20confidence%20and%20psychological%20resilience%2C%20Warner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20take%20that%20time%20off%20for%20themself%2C%20they're%20able%20to%20reevaluate%20their%20values%20and%20what's%20important%20to%20them%2C%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20that%20strengthens%20their%20identity%20and%20self-worth%2C%26quot%3B%20Warner%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20actually%20provides%20a%20sense%20of%20autonomy%20and%20control%20over%20one's%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarner%20added%20that%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20being%20forced%20into%20a%20job%20that%20doesn't%20fit%20can%20lead%20to%20feelings%20of%20helplessness%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20it's%20a%20risk-reward%20analysis%20individuals%20have%20to%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reward%20for%20taking%20a%20job%20could%20be%20financial%20stability%2C%20but%20the%20risk%20could%20be%20feeling%20unfulfilled%20or%20experiencing%20anxiety%20and%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20individuals%20are%20recognizing%20the%20risks%20far%20outweigh%20the%20rewards%2C%20and%20in%20turn%20are%20choosing%20a%20different%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-being-a-neet-can-be-a-psychological-win-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719571476000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667e832bd1c84a0eaca8974f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-being-a-neet-can-be-a-psychological-win-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20not%20engaged%20in%20employment%2C%20education%2C%20or%20training%20may%20be%20saving%20themselves%20stress%20down%20the%20line%2C%20according%20to%20a%20psychologist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-being-a-neet-can-be-a-psychological-win-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hemant%20Soren%20Leaves%20Jail%20After%205%20Months%20After%20Securing%20Bail%20In%20Land%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEx-Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fhemant-soren%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHemant%20Soren%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20released%20from%20jail%20after%20he%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20in%20a%20land%20scam%20case%20this%20morning.%20%26quot%3BBail%20is%20granted.%20The%20court%20held%2C%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20is%20not%20guilty%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20likelihood%20of%20the%20petitioner%20committing%20an%20offence%20on%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20counsel%2C%20Arunabh%20Chowdhury%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20there%20are%20no%20other%20cases%20against%20him%20at%20this%20time%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20may%20be%20released%20soon.%20Bail%20was%20granted%20on%20payment%20of%20a%20bail%20bond%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%20two%20sureties%20of%20the%20same%20amount%20each..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20leader%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fenforcement-directorate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%2031%20on%20money%20laundering%20charges.%20The%20ED%20has%20accused%20him%20of%20running%20a%20scheme%20to%20manipulate%20records%2C%20via%20fictitious%20transactions%20and%20forged%20documents%2C%20and%20acquire%208.86%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Ranchi%20worth%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20court%20said%20%26quot%3B...broad%20probabilities%20(of%20the%20case)%20do%20not%20specifically%2C%20or%20indirectly%2C%20assign%20the%20petitioner%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20acquisition%20and%20possession%2C%20as%20well%20as%20concealment%20(of%20land)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReasoning%20that%20%26quot%3Bnone%20of%20the%20revenue%20records%20bare%20imprint%20of%20direct%20involvement%20of%20petitioner%20in%20acquisition%20and%20possession%20of%20said%20land%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20the%20ED's%20claim%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20be%20ambiguous%20when%20considered%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20allegation%20the%20land%20was%20already%20acquired%20and%20possessed%20by%20petitioner...%20from%20year%202010%20onwards%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20reasoned%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20likelihood%20of%20the%20petitioner%20committing%20a%20similar%20nature%20of%20offence%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20twin%20conditions%20for%20grant%20of%20bail%20under%20the%20PMLA%20had%2C%20therefore%2C%20been%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20has%20repeatedly%20denied%20the%20charges%20against%20him%2C%20and%20has%20accused%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20of%20framing%20his%20arrest%20-%20which%20was%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20to%20derail%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bail%20order%20today%20comes%20after%20setbacks%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-court-rejects-hemant-sorens-bail-in-land-scam-case-5652958%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERanchi%20special%20court%20had%20denied%20Mr%20Soren%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20rejecting%20a%20plea%20to%20quash%20his%20arrest.%20The%20court%20pointed%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Babundance%20of%20documents%20that%20lay%20foundation%20for%20the%20arrest%20and%20remand%20of%20petitioner%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20was%20also%20told%20he%20could%20not%20%26quot%3Bwiggle%20out%20of%20the%20mess%20he%20created%20for%20himself'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20refused%20interim%20bail%3B%20this%20was%20sought%20on%20grounds%20Mr%20Soren%20needed%20to%20campaign%20for%20his%20party%2C%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-interim-bail-yet-for-hemant-soren-he-had-cited-arvind-kejriwals-example-5651839%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENo%20Interim%20Bail%20Yet%20For%20Hemant%20Soren.%20He%20Cited%20Kejriwal's%20Example%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20hearing%20the%20ED%20argued%20Mr%20Soren%20had%20tried%20to%20subvert%20the%20investigation%20by%20%26quot%3Bmisusing%20state%20machinery%26quot%3B%20and%20so%20opposed%20his%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20prayer%26quot%3B%20for%20interim%20bail%20to%20campaign%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmisusing-state-machinery-probe-agency-opposes-hemant-sorens-bail-in-supreme-court-5706801%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BMisused%20State%20Machinery%26quot%3B%3A%20ED%20On%20Soren's%20Top%20Court%20Bail%20Plea%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20setback%20meant%20Hemant%20Soren%20-%20unlike%20his%20Delhi%20counterpart%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20but%20given%20interim%20bail%20by%20the%20top%20court%20-%20could%20not%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20had%20been%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20top%20court%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20leader%20was%20forced%20to%20withdraw%20another%20Supreme%20Court%20plea%20-%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20-%20after%20tough%20questions%20over%20non-disclosure%20of%20facts%3B%20the%20focus%20was%20on%20not%20revealing%20that%20the%20special%20court%20-%20which%20hears%20money%20laundering%20cases%20-%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20complaint%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-withdraws-bail-petition-after-supreme-court-rap-5718838%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHemant%20Soren's%202%20Bail%20Pleas%20And%20A%20Rap%20By%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20central%20agency%20and%20sought%20its%20response%20to%20an%20interim%20bail%20plea%20filed%20before%20it%20on%20grounds%20the%20High%20Court%20was%20delaying%20delivery%20of%20its%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-probe-agency-claimed-in-its-chargesheet-against-hemant-soren-5378301%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E9%20Acre%20Illegal%20Land%2C%20BMW%20Car%3A%20What%20Report%20On%20Soren's%20Claims%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemant%20Soren%20resigned%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20on%20January%2031%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20ED%20began%20a%20marathon%20ques