sessions%20of%20Parliament%20with%20a%20minimum%20of%20100%20days%20of%20sittings%20a%20year%20for%20each%20House.%20The%20number%20of%20sittings%20per%20year%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20reduced%20from%20an%20average%20of%20121%20days%20(1952-1970)%20to%2070%20days%20per%20year%20since%202000.%20In%202019%2C%20your%20columnist%20introduced%20a%20Private%20Member's%20Bill%20seeking%20a%20fixed%20calendar%20for%20Parliament%20sessions%20and%20a%20minimum%20number%20of%20sittings%20of%20100%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Deputy%20Speaker%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2093%20of%20the%20Constitution%20says%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20shall%20choose%20two%20members%20of%20the%20House%20as%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be.%20The%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20did%20not%20have%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20for%20its%20entire%20five-year%20term.%20The%20Deputy%20Speaker%20is%20not%20subordinate%20to%20the%20Speaker.%20The%20Speaker%20has%20to%20tender%20his%20resignation%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20if%20s%2Fhe%20chooses%20to%20do%20so.%20Traditionally%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20is%20appointed%20from%20the%20Opposition.%20The%20Deputy%20Speaker%20should%20be%20appointed%20in%20this%20session%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Pre-Legislative%20Consultation%20Policy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPre-Legislative%20Consultation%20Policy%20was%20adopted%20in%202014%20to%20ensure%20public%20consultation%20for%20all%20legislation.%20In%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20nine%20out%20of%2010%20bills%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20have%20been%20marked%20by%20zero%20or%20incomplete%20consultations.%20Each%20Minister%2C%20while%20introducing%20a%20Bill%2C%20should%20lay%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20summary%20of%20the%20consultations.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Scrutiny%20Of%20Bills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2014th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20six%20out%20of%2010%20bills%20were%20sent%20to%20various%20committees%20for%20scrutiny%3B%20in%20the%2015th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20it%20was%20seven%20out%20of%2010.%20This%20figure%20fell%20in%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20four%20out%20of%2010.%20In%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20about%20one%20out%20of%20five%20bills%20was%20sent%20for%20scrutiny.%20Abysmal.%20The%20National%20Commission%20to%20Review%20the%20Working%20of%20the%20Constitution%20(2002)%20recommended%20that%20all%20bills%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20should%20first%20be%20examined%20by%20the%20relevant%20committee.%20Committees%20should%20also%20review%20the%20implementation%20of%20laws%20passed%20by%20Parliament.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Constitution%20Amendment%20Bills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20constitutional%20committee%20from%20both%20Houses%20should%20be%20formed%20to%20review%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20Constitution%20Amendment%20Bills%20before%20they%20are%20introduced.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Admit%20267%20Notice%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERule%20267%20gives%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20a%20written%20notice%20to%20suspend%20regular%20business%20and%20seek%20an%20immediate%20discussion%20on%20an%20issue%20of%20national%20importance.%20It%20has%20been%20eight%20years%20since%20such%20a%20discussion%20has%20been%20permitted.%20At%20least%20one%20such%20notice%20should%20be%20admitted%20in%20each%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Active%20Participation%20Of%20PM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20not%20answered%20a%20single%20question%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20Parliament.%20His%20participation%20has%20been%20limited%20to%20monologues%20-%20speeches%20during%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%2C%20farewells%2C%20and%20special%20occasions.%20Narendra%20Modi%20needs%20to%20answer%20questions%2C%20take%20part%20in%20debates%20and%20discussions%20on%20national%20issues.%20(The%20UK%20Parliament%20has%20Prime%20Minister's%20Question%20Time%20every%20Wednesday%20where%20it%20is%20mandatory%20for%20the%20PM%20to%20answer.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20On%20Security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Committee%20on%20security%20in%20Parliament%20house%20complex%20should%20be%20reconstituted%20immediately%2C%20with%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20as%20the%20Chairperson.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20Committee%20On%20National%20Economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20on%20National%20Economy%20should%20be%20formed%20to%20produce%20annual%20reports%20on%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy.%20The%20report%20should%20then%20be%20discussed%20in%20Parliament.%20The%20National%20Commission%20to%20Review%20the%20Working%20of%20the%20Constitution%20(2002)%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20system%20for%20Parliamentary%20scrutiny%20of%20public%20borrowing.%20Since%20it%20affects%20future%20governments%2C%20beyond%20certain%20limits%2C%20borrowing%20proposals%20should%20also%20be%20reviewed%20by%20the%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20on%20National%20Economy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%20Technical%20Expertise%20for%20Committees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFunds%20should%20be%20allocated%20to%20provide%20research%20support%20staff%20to%20committees%20to%20conduct%20public%20hearings%2C%20inquiries%2C%20and%20collect%20data.%20Currently%2C%20the%20secretariat%20assists%20with%20scheduling%20meetings%20and%20taking%20notes.%20The%20quality%20of%20output%20will%20improve%20if%20each%20committee%20is%20assigned%20a%20team%20dedicated%20to%20research.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlease%20open%20the%20door%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENothing%20is%20different%2C%20we've%20been%20here%20before%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPacing%20these%20halls%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrying%20to%20talk%20over%20the%20silence%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnd%20pride%20sticks%20out%20its%20tongue%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELaughs%20at%20the%20portrait%20that%20we've%20become%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EStuck%20in%20a%20frame%2C%20unable%20to%20change%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20was%20wrong%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDid%20I%20wait%20too%20long%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20turn%20the%20lights%20back%20on%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Billy%20Joel%2C%20%3Cem%3ETurn%20the%20Lights%20Back%20On.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Additional%20Research%3A%20Ayashman%20Dey%2C%20Anagha.)%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719570300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fo3a9r0oo_modi-billy_625x300_28_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fheres-an-unlikely-combination-narendra-modi-and-billy-joel-5987169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20verdict%20after%20India%20Elections%202024%20is%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20must%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20turned%20into%20a%20deep%2C%20dark%20chamber.%20Turn%20the%20Lights%20Back%20On.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fheres-an-unlikely-combination-narendra-modi-and-billy-joel-5987169%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fheres-an-unlikely-combination-narendra-modi-and-billy-joel-5987169%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fheres-an-unlikely-combination-narendra-modi-and-billy-joel-5987169%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22While%20I%20lived%20in%20Panama%2C%20my%20son%20got%202%20summer%20breaks.%20Summer%20vacation%20is%20different%20there%20than%20it%20is%20in%20the%20US.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223061%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20boy%20wearing%20a%20tie-dye%20shirt%20riding%20a%20bike%20near%20an%20ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c333040cf2af6e4f5e456%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222642%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStephanie%20Kaloi's%20son%20(not%20pictured)%20split%20time%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Panama%20for%20two%20years.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20lived%20in%20Panama%20for%20two%20years%20and%20my%20son%20split%20time%20between%20there%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20got%20to%20enjoy%20two%20summer%20vacations%3B%20one%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20one%20in%20Panama.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20no%20longer%20live%20there%2C%20but%20I'm%20thankful%20for%20the%20experiences%20we%20had.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20May%202021%2C%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-moving-to-panama-new-mexico-hamptons-best-places-move-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emoved%20to%20Panama%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20My%20partner%20and%20I%20lived%20there%20for%20two%20years%2C%20and%20during%20that%20time%2C%20my%20son%20would%20spend%20one%20month%20with%20us%20and%20one%20month%20with%20his%20dad%20and%20stepmother%20in%20the%20States.%20This%20was%20possible%20only%20because%20he%20has%20been%20homeschooled%20since%20first%20grade%2C%20and%20his%20dad%20and%20I%20established%20a%20system%20to%20keep%20his%20work%20in%20both%20homes%20synchronized.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20experience%20was%20hectic%20and%20difficult%20at%20times%2C%20but%20I%20am%20a%20big%20believer%20in%20experiencing%20different%20countries%2C%20cultures%2C%20and%20people%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20the%20idea%20that%20sometimes%20you%20have%20to%20take%20a%20big%20leap%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed234c37-fb22-41d7-9394-a5279dbdde61%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKids%20start%20their%20summer%20vacation%20mid-December%20in%20Panama%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20learned%20a%20lot%20during%20our%20time%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20more%20pleasant%20surprises%20was%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-vacation-evolution-over-the-years-photos-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esummer%20vacation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20there%20generally%20begins%20in%20mid-December%20(at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20rainy%20season)%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20trimester%20of%20school.%20School%20doesn't%20pick%20back%20up%20again%20until%20February.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20schedule%20created%20an%20interesting%20opportunity%20for%20my%20son%2C%20who%20was%20about%20to%20be%2012%20when%20he%20experienced%20his%20first%20summer%20in%20Panama.%20Besides%20how%20incredible%20it%20was%20to%20play%20in%20the%20ocean%20and%20wear%20short%20sleeves%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20January%2C%20he%20also%20found%20himself%20surrounded%20by%20kids%20everywhere%20we%20went%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20he%20hadn't%20always%20experienced%20in%20his%20time%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ff87768-ea36-4f18-9cc0-cb01cc19ca3a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son%20got%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20playing%20with%20kids%20during%20the%20summer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPanama's%20schools%20run%20on%20a%20trimester%20system%2C%20and%20the%20trimesters%20typically%20run%20from%20February%20to%20June%2C%20June%20to%20September%2C%20and%20September%20to%20December.%20For%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20school%20year%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20few%20friends%20for%20him%20through%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-20-year-anniversary-expat-positive-negative-impact-life-abroad-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFacebook%20groups%20for%20expat%20families%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We%20connected%20with%20other%20homeschooled%20children%20from%20France%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20Germany%2C%20but%20he%20had%20a%20harder%20time%20making%20friends%20with%20Panamanian%20children%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20spending%20much%20time%20with%20them%20at%20all.%20The%20added%20challenges%20of%20language%20barriers%20and%20adjusting%20to%20a%20new%20home%20in%20a%20new%20country%20for%20only%20half%20the%20year%20didn't%20help.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20summer%20in%20Panama%20brought%20about%20new%20opportunities%20for%20hanging%20out%20with%20kids.%20He%20didn't%20sign%20up%20for%20any%20camps%20or%20programs%20(at%20the%20time%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-fluent-spanish-english-how-to-do-it-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehis%20Spanish%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20very%20new)%2C%20but%20he%20also%20didn't%20shy%20away%20from%20getting%20to%20know%20kids%20at%20the%20parks%2C%20playgrounds%2C%20and%20when%20we%20were%20out%20at%20local%20events.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20first%20January%20in%20Panama%20offered%20a%20respite%20from%20the%20newness%20of%20it%20all%3B%20he%20could%20spend%20a%20little%20time%20just%20being%20a%20kid%20with%20other%20kids.%20It%20was%20comforting%20to%20find%20that%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenglish-teacher-on-how-to-teach-kids-second-language-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elanguage%20barrier%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20didn't%20always%20matter%20when%20two%20(or%20more)%20kids%20could%20bond%20over%20play%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20we%20were.%20He%20had%20some%20schoolwork%20to%20work%20on%20to%20maintain%20his%20participation%20in%20classes%20in%20the%20States%2C%20but%20we%20focused%20on%20keeping%20things%20light%20so%20he%20could%20have%20more%20unstructured%20time%20to%20experience%20what%20was%20around%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246e31a3d-c6e8-4604-9360-52246b180e9d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20we%20lived%20in%20Panama%2C%20my%20son%20got%20two%20summers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaking%20a%20major%20change%20or%20move%20is%20almost%20always%20a%20challenge%2C%20and%20doing%20so%20when%20you're%20not%20even%20a%20teenager%20yet%20takes%20mental%20and%20emotional%20fortitude%20that%20not%20everyone%20has.%20Though%20our%20long-term%20plans%20in%20Panama%20didn't%20work%20out%20the%20way%20we%20imagined%2C%20and%20now%20we%20split%20our%20time%20evenly%20between%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-mom-in-france-differences-in-parenting-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20US%20and%20France%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20years%20we%20spent%20there%20were%20unique%20and%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20in%20no%20small%20part%20due%20to%20the%20summers%20my%20son%20experienced%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20time%20summer%20rolled%20around%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20most%20Panamanian%20children%20were%20back%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%20and%20the%20rainy%20season%20was%20rolling%20in.%20In%20a%20sense%2C%20my%20son%20got%20to%20experience%20the%20best%20of%20both%20homes%3A%20friends%20in%20each%20spot%2C%20plenty%20to%20see%20and%20do%2C%20and%20two%20summers%20to%20be%20as%20free%20as%20he%20wanted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin