Farticleshow%2F111338105.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111338105.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8BThe%20Bollywood%20power%20couple%20captivated%20fans%20with%20their%20impeccable%20airport%20fashion.%20The%20duo%20was%20earlier%20this%20afternoon%2C%20spotted%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20airport%2C%20showcasing%20their%20ability%20to%20effortlessly%20blend%20comfort%20and%20style.%20Kiara%20opted%20for%20a%20minimalist%20yet%20fashionable%20ensemble.%20She%20donned%20a%20white%20crop%20top%20with%20half%20sleeves%2C%20which%20she%20paired%20with%20wide-legged%20denim%20pants.%20Kiara's%20choice%20of%20statement%20brown%20chunky%20boots%20and%20golden%20hoop%20earrings%20added%20a%20trendy%20touch%20to%20her%20outfit%2C%20while%20her%20understated%20makeup%20and%20flowing%20hair%20completed%20the%20look.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsidharth-malhotra-and-kiara-advani-slay-airport-fashion-with-coordinated-looks-video-inside%2Farticleshow%2F111338105.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22D%20Fadnavis%20Tackles%20Opposition's%20%26quot%3BUdta%20Punjab%26quot%3B%20Jibe%20In%20Pune%20Porsche%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20is%20working%20to%20install%20AI-powered%20cameras%20in%20eateries%20across%20Pune%20and%20the%20licences%20of%2070%20pubs%20have%20been%20cancelled%20after%20the%20horrific%20Porsche%20crash%20in%20which%20a%20teen%20driver%20ran%20over%20two%20techies%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20said%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Porsche%20crash%20and%20its%20aftermath%20were%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20massive%20showdown%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPune%20has%20become%20a%20drug%20haven%2C%20the%20Opposition%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETackling%20the%20Opposition's%20key%20question%20-%20what%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20prevent%20such%20accidents%20in%20the%20future%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20also%20the%20state%20Home%20Minister%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20accident%2C%2070%20pub%20licences%20have%20been%20cancelled%20in%20Pune.%20Work%20is%20being%20done%20to%20install%20AI-enabled%20cameras%20to%20know%20when%20the%20establishment%20shuts%20for%20the%20day%2C%20whether%20the%20age%20of%20the%20customer%20was%20checked%20upon%20entry%2C%20and%20what%20proof%20of%20age%20was%20provided%20on%20entry.%20If%20patrons%20are%20allowed%20entry%20without%20proof%2C%20action%20will%20be%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20who%20was%20driving%20the%20Porsche%20on%20May%2019%20was%20seen%20on%20security%20footage%20drinking%20with%20his%20friends%20in%20two%20pubs%2C%20unstopped%20by%20anyone%20though%20he%20is%20underage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition's%20%26quot%3BUdta%20Punjab%26quot%3B%20Charge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leader%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20Vijay%20Waddetiwar%20claimed%20Pune%20is%20becoming%20like%20'Udta%20Punjab'%20-%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20drug%20menace%20in%20the%20border%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPune%20is%20a%20city%20where%20students%20come%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20place%20here%20where%20you%20don't%20get%20drugs.%20This%20car%2C%20which%20was%20without%20a%20number%20plate%2C%20was%20on%20the%20roads%20for%20six%20months.%20How%20did%20the%20police%20allow%20it%20to%20be%20on%20the%20road%20for%20so%20long%3F%20If%20they%20are%20doing%20something%20later%2C%20or%20changing%20blood%20samples%2C%20there%20must%20be%20political%20reasons%20for%20it.%20Rs%205%20lakh%20was%20taken%20as%20hafta%20(extortion%20money)%20from%20rooftop%20hotels%20in%20the%20city%20and%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20from%20smaller%20outlets.%20How%20were%2027%20pubs%20running%20there%20without%20permission%3F%20What%20was%20the%20Police%20Commissioner%20doing%3F%20We%20need%20a%20detailed%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20explosive%20charges%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPune%20is%20the%20IT%20hub%20and%20the%20cultural%20centre%20of%20the%20state.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20should%20not%20liken%20it%20to%20%26quot%3BUdta%20Punjab%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20here%20to%20give%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20anyone.%20The%20police%20have%20taken%20a%20very%20proactive%20approach%20here.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20investigate%20them.%20This%20is%20a%20new%20habit%2C%20someone%20brings%20a%20paper%20and%20talks%20about%20rate%20cards.%20Here%2C%20the%20police%20have%20undertaken%20the%20investigation%20and%20the%20information%20provided%20by%20Mr%20Waddetiwar%20will%20be%20looked%20into%20by%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20car%20without%20a%20number%20plate%20go%20unnoticed%20for%20six%20months%2C%20the%20opposition%20questioned.%20%26quot%3BThey%20had%20registered%20the%20car%20but%20not%20fulfilled%20the%20process.%20The%20tax%20was%20not%20paid.%20We%20will%20look%20into%20it%20and%20see%20if%20any%20RTO%20officers%20are%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20also%20defended%20the%20Pune%20Police%20Commissioner%20and%20said%20that%20he%20has%20done%20a%20very%20proactive%20job%2C%20dismissing%20calls%20for%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accident%20happened%20on%20May%2019%20around%202%3A30%20am.%20The%20accused%20was%20beaten%20by%20the%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20spot%20and%20was%20later%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20The%20police%20filed%20a%20complaint%20under%20Section%20304(a)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(causing%20death%20by%20negligence).%20After%20officials%20said%20that%20Section%20304%20of%20the%20IPC%20(culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder)%20should%20be%20filed%2C%20it%20was%20added%20to%20the%20case%20diary%20the%20same%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%2C%20defending%20the%20police%20action%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20very%20clearly%20mentioned%20before%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20that%20the%20boy%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20accident%20and%20he%20is%2017%20years%20old...%20The%20police%20said%20that%20he%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20Nirbhaya%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20that%20if%20a%2017-year-old%20commits%20a%20crime%2C%20he%2Fshe%20can%20be%20treated%20as%20an%20adult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20also%20addressed%20how%20the%20cops%20moved%20in%20promptly%20to%20prevent%20the%20case%20from%20being%20derailed%20by%20a%20blood%20swap.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20no%20alcohol%20was%20found%20in%20the%20teen's%20blood%20sample%2C%20the%20police%20figured%20that%20something%20was%20wrong.%20They%20took%20the%20teen's%20DNA%20and%20that%20of%20his%20family.%20The%20match%20returned%20positive%20with%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20continued.%20Several%20people%20were%20arrested%2C%20including%20a%20doctor.%20One%20of%20the%20arrested%20accused%20confessed%20to%20taking%20Rs%203%20lakh%20to%20swap%20out%20the%20sample%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20this%2C%20a%20chargesheet%20was%20filed%20and%20legal%20evidence%20was%20prepared.%20The%20crash%20impact%20analysis%20was%20investigated%2C%20and%20we%20knew%20that%20the%20lock%20speed%20after%20he%20pressed%20the%20brakes%20was%20110%20kmph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20along%20the%20route%20the%20teen%20took%20and%20all%20legal%20and%20technical%20evidence%20are%20put%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20Did%20The%20Police%20Go%20Wrong%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20extending%20the%20government's%20support%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20the%20teen's%20father%20for%20giving%20a%20car%20to%20his%20underage%20son%2C%20against%20the%20bar%20operator%2C%20and%20against%20the%20grandfather%20for%20asking%20their%20driver%20to%20take%20the%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20did%20the%20police%20go%20wrong%3F%20When%20the%20accused%20was%20brought%20in%20at%203%20am%2C%20he%20should%20have%20been%20sent%20for%20a%20medical%20test%20immediately.%20But%20that%20happened%20at%208%3A30%20am.%20Secondly%2C%20when%20such%20crimes%20happen%2C%20they%20usually%20charge%20the%20accused%20under%20Section%20304(a).%20The%20police%20also%20did%20the%20same%20in%20this%20case%20but%20they%20ideally%20should%20have%20informed%20the%20seniors.%20Those%20who%20did%20not%20do%20their%20work%20have%20been%20suspended%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20May%2019%2C%20the%20teenager%2C%20who%20had%20been%20drinking%20with%20his%20friends%20in%20two%20pubs%20in%20Pune%20to%20celebrate%20his%20Class%2012%20results%2C%20rammed%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%20into%20a%20two-wheeler%20and%20killed%20two%2024-year-old%20IT%20professionals%20in%20Pune's%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20area.%20Aneesh%20Awadhiya%2C%20who%20was%20riding%20the%20bike%20was%20sent%20flying%20and%20hit%20a%20parked%20car%2C%20while%20Ashwini%20Koshta%20-%20riding%20pillion%20-%20was%20flung%2020%20feet%20into%20the%20air.%20Both%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2017%20years%20and%208%20months%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20four%20months%20short%20of%20the%20legal%20age%20for%20driving%20and%20more%20than%20seven%20years%20shy%20of%20Maharashtra's%20legal%20age%20for%20drinking.%20He%20was%20initially%20granted%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20accident%20and%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20traffic%20safety%20and%20assist%20the%20traffic%20cops.%20Following%20massive%20outrage%20over%20the%20court%20order%2C%20the%20teen%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20remand%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20several%20arrests%20were%20made%20in%20the%20case%2C%20including%20the%20teen's%20parents%20and%20grandfather.%20The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20recently%20ordered%20the%20teen's%20release%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20bound%20by%20law%2C%20the%20aims%20and%20objectives%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20and%20must%20treat%20him%20as%20any%20child%20in%20conflict%20with%20law%20separately%20from%20an%20adult%2C%20despite%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719567960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F2a518j9g_devendra-fadnavis-ani_625x300_28_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-tackles-oppositions-udta-punjab-jibe-in-pune-porsche-crash-5988571%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20is%20working%20to%20install%20AI-powered%20cameras%20in%20eateries%20across%20Pune%20and%20the%20licences%20of%2070%20pubs%20have%20been%20cancelled%20after%20the%20horrific%20Porsche%20crash%20that%20killed%20two%20techies%20last%20month%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20said%20in%20assembly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-tackles-oppositions-udta-punjab-jibe-in-pune-porsche-crash-5988571%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-tackles-oppositions-udta-punjab-jibe-in-pune-porsche-crash-5988571%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22http