20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20doctor%20said%2C%20'It%20looks%20like%20I%20should%20be%20talking%20to%20a%2060-year-old%20man%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2043%2C%20Hintenberger%20said%20that%20transitioning%20to%20a%20vegan%20diet%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%20helped%20her%20manage%20chronic%20illnesses%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fdo-i-have-ibs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eirritable%20bowel%20syndrome%20(IBS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20polycystic%20ovary%20syndrome%20(PCOS).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20athlete%20has%20since%20won%20gold%20medals%20and%20set%20multiple%20world%20records%20in%20kettlebell%20sport%20and%20will%20compete%20at%20upcoming%20events%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplantbuilt.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVegan%20Strong%20PlantBuilt%3C%2Fa%3E%20roster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHintenberger%20said%20habits%20like%20eating%20lots%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpreworkout-foods-fuel-weight-lifting-high-intensity-workouts-sports-dietitian%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efruit%20for%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20worrying%20less%20about%20protein%2C%20and%20avoiding%20digestive%20irritants%20like%20gluten%20help%20her%20feel%20and%20perform%20her%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cff78352-08da-4766-83fc-8da5d25e9dc9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECutting%20out%20dairy%20and%20meat%20helped%20her%20reduce%20bloating%20and%20digestive%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHintenberger%20never%20expected%20she'd%20go%20vegan%2C%20but%20severe%20health%20issues%20made%20her%20desperate%20for%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20this%20journey%20because%20I%20was%20sick%20of%20being%20sick%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20symptoms%20that%20lasted%20weeks%20that%20turned%20into%20months%20that%20turned%20into%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20symptoms%20included%20bloating%2C%20constipation%2C%20acne%20and%20itchiness%2C%20light-headedness%2C%20lethargy%2C%20and%20sleep%20paralysis%2C%20along%20with%20other%20digestive%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20she%20was%20traveling%20with%20a%20client%20and%20was%20in%20so%20much%20pain%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20eat%20normal%20meals%20and%20resorted%20to%20boiling%20prunes%20to%20try%20to%20get%20some%20nutrients%20and%20calories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20wanted%20to%20rip%20my%20skin%20off.%20I%20hated%20being%20in%20my%20own%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20said%20her%20issues%20were%20related%20to%20stress%20but%20also%20poor%20digestion%20and%20recommended%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Ffodmap-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelimination%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHintenberger%20gradually%20cut%20out%20potential%20trigger%20foods%2C%20realizing%20that%20dairy%2C%20meat%2C%20and%20gluten%20had%20been%20worsening%20her%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20she%20was%20concerned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-protein-maximize-muscle-gains-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20enough%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Hintenberger%20found%20that%20she%20didn't%20need%20as%20much%20as%20she%20thought%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlants%20have%20all%20the%20protein%20you%20need%20to%20be%20strong%2C%20to%20be%20healthy%2C%20to%20be%20competitive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20stopped%20tracking%20nutrients%20and%20focused%20on%20eating%20what%20seemed%20to%20work%20best%20for%20her%20body%2C%20prompting%20a%20big%20improvement%20in%20her%20kidney%20issues%2C%20which%20can%20be%20exacerbated%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fcan-you-eat-too-much-protei%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20too%20much%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d0cc85e-40bf-4390-b883-fc153633511f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuitting%20fad%20diets%20helped%20her%20lose%20weight%20and%20boost%20her%20performance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20her%20life%2C%20Hintenberger%20struggled%20with%20food%20addiction%20and%20binge%20eating.%20But%20following%20a%20strict%20high-protein%2C%20low-carb%20diet%20along%20with%20an%20intense%20exercise%20schedule%20didn't%20seem%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20much%20I%20trained%20or%20how%20healthy%20I%20ate%2C%20I%20was%20always%20gaining%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20by%20letting%20go%20of%20her%20weight%20loss%20efforts%20that%20Hintenberg%20saw%20the%20changes%20she%20was%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFocusing%20on%20meeting%20her%20nutritional%20needs%20and%20switching%20to%20a%20plant-based%20diet%20eventually%20helped%20her%20lose%20more%20than%2070%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20showing%20two%20pictures%20of%20a%20woman%20before%20and%20after%20losing%20weight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667d9002d1c84a0eaca85524%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221131%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennifer%20Hintenberger%20said%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20she%20stopped%20trying%20to%20lose%20weight%20and%20focused%20on%20a%20plant-based%20diet%2C%20she%20felt%20healthier%20and%20eventually%20dropped%2070%20pounds.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jennifer%20Hintenberger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20powerful%20thing%20was%20changing%20the%20way%20I%20ate.%20When%20I%20finally%20stopped%20eating%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20I%20lost%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Hintenberger%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20I%20don't%20care%20about%20my%20size%2C%20I%20care%20if%20I%20have%20energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22126dc3d7-8c46-4e8f-9ef5-6b5568bbecf7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20eats%20lots%20of%20fruit%20for%20better%20energy%20and%20performance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20on%20fad%20diets%2C%20Hintenberger%20used%20to%20avoid%20fruit%2C%20fearing%20the%20sugar%20and%20carbs%20would%20cause%20health%20issues%20and%20weight%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20afraid%20of%20fruit%2C%20told%20to%20eat%20high-protein%20and%20low-carb%2C%20that%20fruit%20is%20the%20devil%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20world%20champion%20in%20kettlebell%20sport%2C%20she%20now%20eats%20as%20many%20as%2020%20servings%20of%20fruit%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20typical%20day%20of%20eating%20includes%20a%20green%20smoothie%2C%20bananas%2C%20mangos%2C%20cherries%2C%20and%20often%20lots%20of%20watermelon%20as%20a%20snack.%20She%20rounds%20out%20her%20nutritional%20needs%20with%20her%20staple%20energy%20balls%20made%20from%20almond%20butter%20and%20vegan%20chocolate%20chips.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20she%20has%20hearty%20vegan%20dinners%20like%20curry%2C%20tacos%2C%20or%20Thai%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHintenberger%20said%20eating%20a%20plant-based%20diet%20has%20helped%20her%20recover%20more%20quickly%20from%20exercise%2C%20and%20continue%20gaining%20strength%20so%20she%20can%20stay%20at%20the%20top%20of%20her%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20never%20one%20to%20push%20veganism%2C%20but%20I%20genuinely%20want%20to%20be%20an%20example%20of%20health%20as%20we%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvegan-athlete-plant-based-diet-helped-manage-ibs-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719565202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667db24340cf2af6e4f65de6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%