%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcanopy-inaugurated-in-2009-congress-bjp-blame-each-other-over-delhi-airport-roof-collapse%2Farticleshow%2F111335291.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Even%20Write...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Raps%20Bihar%20Teachers%20Over%20'Skip%20Test'%20Request%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPanchayat%20teachers%20from%20Bihar%20government%20schools%20who%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20exemption%20from%20a%20competency%20test%20introduced%20by%20the%20state%20government%20in%202023%20-%20if%20they%20want%20to%20continue%20working%20-%20returned%20home%20empty-handed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20strong%20remarks%20criticised%20the%20teachers%20for%20even%20thinking%20they%20can%20skip%20the%20competency%20test%2C%20and%20upheld%20the%20state%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20the%20level%20of%20education%20in%20the%20country%3F%20A%20postgraduate%20who%20gets%20a%20job%20and%20cannot%20even%20write%20an%20application%20for%20leave%3F%20When%20a%20state%20like%20Bihar%20tries%20to%20improve%20this%20system%20and%20conducts%20a%20qualifying%20examination%20for%20this%2C%20it%20is%20opposed%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20said%20on%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20non-profit%20Parivartankari%20Prarambhik%20Sikshak%20Sangh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20teachers%20help%20build%20the%20nation%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20can't%20face%20these%20(competency)%20tests%2C%20then%20you%20should%20resign.%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20then%20upheld%20a%20decision%20of%20the%20Patna%20High%20Court%20and%20dismissed%20the%20petitions%20against%20the%20state%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20Education%20Department%20in%202023%2C%20using%20powers%20under%20Article%20309%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20had%20made%20rules%20for%20teachers%20employed%20by%20panchayats%20and%20local%20bodies%20and%20made%20them%20equivalent%20to%20school%20teachers%20recruited%20under%20the%20Bihar%20State%20School%20Teachers%20(Appointment%2C%20Transfer%2C%20Disciplinary%20Action%20and%20Service%20Conditions)%20Rules%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20state%20also%20made%20another%20rule%20for%20the%20qualifying%20examination%20-%20a%20computer-based%20one%20conducted%20by%20the%20Bihar%20School%20Examination%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20four%20lakh%20panchayat%20teachers%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20also%20said%20that%20unless%20the%20contract%20teachers%20pass%20the%20eligibility%20test%2C%20no%20teacher%20can%20continue%20working.%20It%20was%20against%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20high%20court%20that%20the%20teachers%20filed%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719561960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Far9jdb9g_supreme-court_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-even-write-application-for-leave-supreme-court-raps-bihar-teachers-over-skip-test-request-5988284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Panchayat%20teachers%20from%20Bihar%20government%20schools%20who%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20exemption%20from%20a%20competency%20test%20introduced%20by%20the%20state%20government%20in%202023%20-%20if%20they%20want%20to%20continue%20working%20-%20returned%20home%20empty-handed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-even-write-application-for-leave-supreme-court-raps-bihar-teachers-over-skip-test-request-5988284%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-even-write-application-for-leave-supreme-court-raps-bihar-teachers-over-skip-test-request-59882