ed%20to%20international%20fame%20and%20earnings%3F%20That%20is%20the%20question%20on%20everyone's%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20Nag%20Ashwin%20comes%20with%20a%20reputation.%20He%20created%20magic%20with%20%3Cem%3EMahanati%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20biopic%20on%20yesteryear%20actress%20Savitri%2C%20and%20won%20hearts%20and%20awards.%20And%20this%20is%20just%20his%20third%20film%20in%2010%20years%20as%20working%20as%20a%20director.%20You%20need%20tremendous%20self-confidence%20to%20dare%20to%20dream%20this%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalki%20manages%20to%20take%20the%20story%20across%20centuries%2C%20transcend%20from%20a%20mythological%20Mahabharatha%20into%20a%20tech-savvy%20distant%20future%2C%20without%20too%20much%20of%20a%20fuss%20or%20transition%20issue%2C%20using%20computer%20graphics%20and%20real-world%20art%2C%20quite%20seamlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20was%20war%20and%20death%20from%20the%20battlefield%20aeons%20ago%2C%20the%20fast-forward%20into%20the%20future%20is%20even%20more%20depressing.%20At%20least%20there%20was%20a%20Krishna%20and%20an%20Ashwattamma%20and%20a%20dharma%20that%20guided%20actions%20and%20events%20then.%20Now%20it%20is%20a%20wait%20for%20a%20dismal%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ageing%2C%20shrivelled%20God%20of%20The%20Complex%20who%20wants%20to%20get%20the%20ambrosia%20of%20power%20and%20youthfulness%20by%20drawing%20the%20life%20force%20out%20of%20babies%20still%20forming%20in%20a%20mother's%20womb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20seem%20that%20even%20in%20future%2C%20women%20have%20no%20control%20over%20their%20own%20bodies.%20They%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20power%20structure%2C%20their%20only%20role%20is%20to%20conceive%20and%20nurture.%20So%20you%20can%20catapult%2Fzoom%20a%20thousand%20years%20into%20the%20future%20and%20you%20still%20find%20sexual%20harassment%20in%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Deepika%20Padukone%20to%20Disha%20Patani%2C%20Shobana%20to%20Mrunal%20Thakur%2C%20the%20one%20who%20stood%20out%20for%20me%20was%20the%20bright%20young%20Malayalam%20actress%20Anna%20Ben%20of%20Kumbalangi%20Nights%20fame.%20I%20would%20have%20hoped%20for%20a%20stronger%20character%20for%20the%20woman%20who%20would%20be%20the%20mother%20to%20God%20Kalki.%20With%20two%20young%20women%20as%20the%20film's%20producers%2C%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20see%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabhas%20himself%20is%20not%20out%20and%20out%20the%20goody-goody%20superhero.%20He%20has%20human%20frailties%2C%20is%20willing%20to%20sacrifice%20even%20his%20godfather%20to%20protect%20himself%2C%20is%20laidback%2C%20selfish%2C%20doesn't%20want%20to%20move%20or%20act%20unless%20he%20feels%20threatened%2C%20and%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20truly%20ignites%20him%20is%20the%20desire%20to%20go%20to%20%60The%20Complex'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20interesting%20that%20in%20our%20futuristic%20world%2C%20the%20ultimate%20aspiration%20is%20for%20a%20green%20world%2C%20with%20real%20plants%20and%20animals%2C%20real%20fruits%20and%20food.%20But%20Prabhas's%20world%20looks%20grey%2C%20dismal%20and%20desertified%2C%20with%20bad%20roads%20too%2C%20and%20the%20only%20thing%20people%20seem%20interested%20in%20is%20accumulating%20points.%20A%20parallel%20to%20our%20money-driven%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20has%20consciously%20introduced%20diversity%20in%20the%20population%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20rebel%20world%2C%20which%20is%20fighting%20for%20a%20better%20tomorrow%2C%20perhaps%20to%20make%20it%20a%20global%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmitabh%20Bachchan%20is%20the%20connecting%20thread%20from%20the%20beginning%20into%20the%20future%2C%20and%20as%20expected%2C%20he%20brings%20gravitas%20to%20his%20role%20and%20responsibility%2C%20easily%20looking%20the%20better%20of%20the%20two%20in%20the%20fight%20sequences%20with%20Prabhas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20half%20is%20all%20about%20introducing%20the%20Kalki%20universe%2C%20the%20rules%20of%20living%20and%20existence.%20Cameos%20by%20Dulquer%20Salman%2C%20Mrinal%20Thakur%2C%20Vijay%20Devarakonda%2C%20add%20not%20just%20to%20the%20star%20weight%20but%20also%20to%20the%20story%20of%20the%20film%2C%20but%20the%20surprise%20elements%20are%20Ram%20Gopal%20Varma%20and%20a%20Rajamouli.%20They%20evoke%20laughter%20and%20lighten%20up%20the%20mood%20but%20I%20wondered%20how%20much%20a%20non-telugu%20audience%20would%20connect%20to%20the%20contextual%20humour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20specially%20designed%20futuristic%20car%20Bujji%20is%20almost%20a%20character%20in%20the%20film%2C%20with%20Keerthy%20Suresh%2C%20lending%20the%20voice%20for%20the%20AI-driven%20robot%20that%20displays%20emotional%20intelligence%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamal%20Haasan%20does%20not%20get%20too%20much%20screen%20time%2C%20but%20then%20the%20challenger%20to%20God%20had%20to%20be%20someone%20like%20him.%20No%20ordinary%20actor%20may%20be%20acceptable%20in%20that%20role.%20That%20is%20why%2C%20the%20sequel%20will%20be%20eagerly%20awaited%2C%20where%20we%20can%20expect%20Kamal%20Haasan's%20character%20to%20get%20meatier%20with%20confrontations%20set%20up%20between%20him%2C%20the%20Big%20B%20and%20the%20Rebel%20Star%20Prabhas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Uma%20Sudhir%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719558180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fptskvld_kalki_625x300_28_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fwill-kalki-2898-ad-do-a-bahubali-or-rrr-5987651%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Billed%20as%20the%20most%20expensive%20Indian%20film%20at%20Rs%20600%20crore%2C%20will%20Kalki%20be%20able%20to%20do%20a%20Baahubali%2C%20an%20RRR%2C%20or%20a%20Pushpa%3F%20Will%20it%20find%20pride%20of%20place%20among%20those%20films%20from%20Tollywood%20that%20have%20catapulted%20to%20intern