n%20has%20already%20caused%20substantial%20waterlogging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShelly%20Oberoi%20had%20previously%20assured%20that%20the%20storm%20drains%20were%20clean%20and%20ready%2C%20promising%20a%20hassle-free%20monsoon%20for%20Delhi%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20intersections%20like%20ITO%20saw%20about%20two%20to%20three%20feet%20of%20water%20accumulation%2C%20causing%20extensive%20traffic%20jams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hanuman%20Temple%20Intersection%20leading%20to%20Mandi%20House%20was%20submerged%20under%20three%20feet%20of%20water%2C%20leading%20to%20road%20closures%20and%20disruptions%20on%20Ashoka%20Road%2C%20Feroz%20Shah%20Road%2C%20and%20Connaught%20Place.%20Similar%20conditions%20were%20reported%20at%20Moolchand%20and%20other%20areas%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Noida%2C%20the%20situation%20was%20equally%20dire.%20Despite%20inspections%20by%20the%20CEO%20of%20Noida%20Authority%20and%20officials%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20rain%20caused%20severe%20waterlogging%20in%20many%20areas%2C%20including%20the%20Mahamaya%20Flyover%2C%20Sector%2062%2C%20and%20Sector%2015%20and%2016.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719557820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fln8p8brk_delhi-rain-waterlogging-after-heavy-rain-pti_625x300_28_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-ncr-submerges-as-torrential-rain-breaks-88-year-old-record-5987793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Torrential%20rainfall%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20that%20started%20yesterday%2C%20led%20to%20widespread%20waterlogging%20and%20severe%20traffic%20jams%20this%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-ncr-submerges-as-torrential-rain-break