mand%20For%20NEET%20Discussion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20today%20demanded%20to%20discuss%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20the%20alleged%20leak%20of%20the%20medical%20exam%20NEET-UG%20and%20other%20sought-after%2C%20competitive%20tests.%20The%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20has%20said%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20answer%20any%20question%20on%20the%20exam%20controversies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20house%20business%20began%20this%20morning%2C%20Congress%20MP%20KC%20Venugopal%20submitted%20an%20adjournment%20motion%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20discuss%20unprecedented%20cases%20of%20paper%20leaks%20including%20NEET-UG%20and%20UGC-NET.%20The%20Opposition%20wants%20to%20point%20out%20%26quot%3Bfailures%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20which%20conducts%20over%20a%20dozen%20competitive%20national%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20received%2022%20notices%20on%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20case.%20The%20President%20has%20already%20indicated%20in%20her%20speech%20in%20paragraph%2020%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20fair%20investigation%20in%20the%20irregularities%20in%20NEET%2C%26quot%3B%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20said%2C%20and%20adjourned%20the%20house%20till%2012%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20session%20resumed%2C%20the%20Speaker%20adjourned%20the%20session%20till%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20leaders%20should%20send%20a%20message%20from%20parliament%20that%20all%20the%20parties%20are%20concerned%20about%20students%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20who%20are%20worried%20about%20their%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20discuss%20the%20issue%20calmly.%20Both%20Opposition%20and%20ruling%20alliance%20should%20send%20a%20common%20message%20to%20students%20from%20parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20too%2C%20asked%20to%20discuss%20the%20NEET%20issue%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Syed%20Naseer%20Hussain%20gave%20a%20'suspension%20of%20business%20notice'%2C%20which%20said%20the%20house%20should%20stop%20all%20activity%20and%20discuss%20only%20the%20NEET-UG%20and%20UGC-NET%20row%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20called%20for%20scrapping%20the%20NEET.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20on%20June%2023%20filed%20a%20criminal%20case%20over%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20NEET-UG%20by%20the%20NTA%20and%20formed%20special%20teams%20to%20probe%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20was%20held%20on%20May%205%3B%20over%2023%20lakh%20candidates%20appeared.%20An%20unprecedented%2067%20candidates%20achieved%20a%20perfect%20score%20of%20720%20marks%20out%20of%20720%2C%20which%20led%20to%20widespread%20protests%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719557040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9mga7t98_lok-sabha-generic-ani-_625x300_26_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-seeks-neet-discussion-in-parliament-ready-says-government-5987364%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Opposition%20today%20demanded%20to%20discuss%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20the%20alleged%20leak%20of%20the%20medical%20exam%20NEET-UG%20and%20other%20sought-after%2C%20competitive%20tests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-seeks-neet-discussion-in-parliament-ready-says-government-5987364%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-seeks-neet-discussion-in-parliament-ready-says-government-5987364%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-seeks-neet-discussion-in-parliament-ready-say