4%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-20-at-11.59.14-1719322998-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354319%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETaruni%E2%80%99s%20life%20goals%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20referred%20to%20YouTube%20videos%20and%20prepared%20notes%20based%20on%20them.%20With%20just%20four%20months%20of%20preparation%20for%20the%20prelims%20and%20two%20months%20for%20the%20mains%2C%20she%20cleared%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353815%2Fias-officer-ashish-kumar-singhal-jaipur-cleared-upsc-cse-after-four-failures-topper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20CSE%20prelims%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20secured%20rank%2014%20in%20the%20Consolidated%20Reserve%20List%20in%20the%20CSE%20mains%202021.%20She%20is%20currently%20an%20officer%20in%20training%20with%20the%20Indian%20Communications%20Finance%20Services%20(IP%26amp%3BTAFS)%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20planned%20her%20studies%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETips%20for%20creating%20an%20effective%20study%20plan%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaruni%20Pandey%20(34)%2C%20a%20proponent%20of%20self-study%20since%20childhood%2C%20always%20relied%20on%20putting%20things%20on%20paper.%20Her%20timetable%20was%20not%20based%20on%20strict%20timings%20but%20rather%20on%20a%20to-do%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20made%20weekly%20and%20monthly%20plans.%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20remember%20is%20to%20be%20flexible%20as%20things%20change%20at%20any%20given%20point%20in%20time.%20I%20used%20to%20have%20a%20daily%20target%20of%20finishing%2C%20say%2C%20a%20chapter%20or%20a%20particular%20portion%20of%20a%20subject%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taruni%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20daily%20plan%20included%20a%2