20but%20merely%20a%20part%20of%20the%20bigger%20plan.%20It%20keeps%20you%20grounded.%20Any%20type%20of%20meditation%20or%20journaling%20keeps%20you%20sane%20during%20this%20hard%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taruni's%20hand-drawn%20timetable%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354346%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETaruni%E2%80%99s%20hand-drawn%20timetable.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWrite%20it%20on%20paper!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaruni%20has%20always%20jotted%20down%20her%20dreams%2C%20plans%20and%20more.%20She%20urges%20aspirants%20to%20write%20their%20feelings%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20get%20clarity%20when%20you%20see%20things%20organised%20visually%20in%20front%20of%20you.%20Look%20at%20your%20triggers%20with%20an%20open%20mind%20and%20eliminate%20the%20ones%20you%20can%2C%20ma