already%20shifting%20towards%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F278549%2Feco-friendly-biodegradable-disposable-tableware-cutlery-party-buy-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euse-and-throw%20disposable%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20design%20and%20virtue.%20The%20entire%20industry%20embraced%20this%20disposable%20mindset.%20When%20I%20joined%20in%202016%2C%20it%20took%20me%20just%20a%20few%20months%2C%20or%20at%20most%20a%20year%2C%20to%20realise%20that%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20something%20I%20could%20devote%20the%20next%2010%20or%2020%20years%20to.%20Given%20my%20commitment%20to%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20I%20felt%20there%20was%20something%20seriously%20wrong%20with%20this%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20time%20when%20he%20presented%20the%20idea%20to%20his%20family%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20scepticism.%20I%20was%20mocked%20for%20even%20thinking%20it%20was%20possible%2C%20but%20as%20I%20progressed%20with%20my%20research%2C%20my%20father%20came%20around.%20I%20decided%20to%20separate%20myself%20from%20the%20family%20business%20and%20start%20NOTE%2C%20which%20stands%20for%20No%20Offence%20To%20Earth%2C%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMade%20with%20bamboo%2C%20coconut%20shell%20and%20zero%20plastic%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20plastic%20straws%2C%20bags%2C%20and%20bottles%20are%20widely%20discussed%2C%20items%20like%20pens%20are%20rarely%20mentioned.%20However%2C%20the%20plastic%20waste%20from%20pens%20is%20substantial%2C%20comparable%20to%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F187780%2Fbengaluru-woman-initiative-shop-vendors-ditch-plastic-bags-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20straw%20%3C%2Fa%3Eproblem.%20The%20lack%20of%20discussion%20around%20this%20issue%20was%20striking%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20there%20were%20no%20real%20alternatives%20to%20plastic%20pens.%20Some%20efforts%20reduced%20the%20plastic%20content%20by%2050%2C%2070%2C%20or%20even%2088%20percent%2C%20but%20plastic%20was%20still%20present.%20Tests%20showed%20that%20even%20pens%20with%20paper%20bodies%20and%20plastic%20cores%20acted%20like%20laminated%20paper%20cups%2C%20preventing%20full%20biodegradability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20shares%20why%20it%20is%20important%20to%20make%20sustainable%20stationery.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20we%20faced%20was%20that%2095%20percent%20of%20a%20pen%20is%20composed%20of%20non-biodegradable%20materials%2C%20primarily%20plastic%20and%20metal%20mixtures.%20These%20plastics%20are%20often%20different%20types%2C%20such%20as%20PVC%2C%20and%20polycarbonate%2C%20each%20with%20different%20properties.%20The%20damage%20caused%20by%20these%20materials%20is%20significant%20because%20the%20components%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20easily%20disassembled%20and%20recycled%20separately%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20economic%20value%20in%20recycling%20them%2C%20making%20it%20practically%20impossible%20to%20recycle%20these%20pens.%20Consequently%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20biodegrade%20for%20the%20next%20300%20years%20or%20more.%20This%20amplifies%20the%20problem%3A%20with%20an%20annual%20production%20volume%20of%2050%20billion%20pens%2C%20all%20of%20this%20plastic%20waste%20cannot%20be%20recycled%20and%20won%E2%80%99t%20biodegrade%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb