mage%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202193px)%20100vw%2C%202193px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FPhoto-1-min-1718940339.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222193%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akash%20learnt%20cooking%20from%20his%20mother%20and%20grandmother%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FPhoto-1-min-1718940339.jpg%202193w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FPhoto-1-min-1718940339-300x208.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FPhoto-1-min-1718940339-500x346.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FPhoto-1-min-1718940339-768x532.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FPhoto-1-min-1718940339-1536x1064.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FPhoto-1-min-1718940339-2048x1419.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FPhoto-1-min-1718940339-150x104.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221519%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAkash%20learnt%20cooking%20from%20his%20mother%20and%20grandmother.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20Chennai%20resident%20only%20began%20cooking%20regularly%20after%20he%20left%20home%20for%20an%20internship%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20following%20his%20degree%20in%20architecture.%20It%20was%20there%20that%20he%20started%20to%20enjoy%20the%20process%20of%20cooking%20and%20appreciate%20its%20finer%20nuances.%20He%20found%20that%20cooking%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20unwind%20and%20destress%20after%20a%20long%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20it%20took%20him%20a%20few%20more%20years%20to%20realise%20that%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334496%2Fkashmir-rukhsaar-sayeed-masterchef-india-chef-khalis-frozen-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrue%20passion%20lay%20in%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20he%20continued%20to%20experiment%20in%20different%20avenues.%20%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20as%20a%20teaching%20assistant%20at%20an%20architecture%20firm.%20I%20even%20did%20a%20diploma%20in%20animation%20to%20see%20if%20that%20excited%20me.%20After%20trying%20out%20different%20things%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20course%20%E2%80%94%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20food%20design%20in%20Milan%2C%20which%20interested%20me%20deeply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20doing%20something%20in%20the%20food%20domain%20where%20he%20could%20use%20his%20creativity%20and%20artistry%20motivated%20Akash.%20After%20completing%20his%20degree%2C%20he%20spent%20a%20year%20travelling%20across%20Europe%2C%20engaging%20in%20various%20internships%20that%20helped%20him%20uncover%20his%20future%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20about%20how%20food%20is%20viewed%20outside%20India.%20I%20worked%20with%20a%20food%20designer%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20but%20what%20I%20missed%20there%20was%20a%20genuine%20connection%20with%20food.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20work%20with%20Italian%20or%20Dutch%20food.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20with%20South%20Indian%20food%20and%20bring%20out%20the%20elements%20of%20our%20cooking%20and%20showcase%20it%20to%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%20wanted%20to%20share%20the%20stories%20and%20history%20behind%20everyday%20food%20in%20a%20modern%20way.%20So%2C%20in%202021%2C%20he%20founded%20%E2%80%98Vizha%20Medai%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20design%20studio%20started%20with%20two%20of%20his%20architecture%20college%20mates.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20multidisciplinary%20studio%20specialising%20in%20event%20design%20and%20decor%2C%20menu%20curation%2C%20outfit%20design%20and%20styling%2C%20and%20creative%20direction.%20They%20curate%20%E2%80%9Cfood%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20art%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20common%20thread%20of%20local%20essence%2C%20says%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWeaving%20a%20story%20around%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20thread%20throughout%20Akash%E2%80%99s%20life%20has%20been%20his%20need%20to%20share%20food%20stories.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%20100-day%20cooking%20project%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20forgotten%20vegetables.%20His%20vision%20for%20participating%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305138%2Fmasterchef-india-contestant-whips-up-gluten-free-desserts-in-her-house-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMasterChef%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tamil%20was%20also%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20share%20the%20story%20of%20South%20Indian%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSouth%20Indian%20cooking%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20offer.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20explored%20as%20much%20as%20it%20should%20be.%20When%20Indian%20food%20is%20spoken%20about%20internationally%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20usually%20identified%20with%20breads%20like%20%3Cem%3Enaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20equivalents%20from%20the%20Southern%20part%20of%20the%20country%20shine%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Akash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20precisely%20what%20he%20did%20during%20the%20show.%20His%20finale%20dish%2C%20which%20included%20a%20main%20course%20and%20dessert%2C%20celebrated%20and%20elevated%20the%20humble%20%3Cem%3Epongal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(made%20with%20rice%20and%20green%20gram)%2C%20both%20savoury%20and%20sweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8KYOJ6SyA6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8KYOJ6SyA6%2F%3Futm_source%3Di